[[File:Chocolate bar detail.png|left|100px]]
A '''chocolate bar''' is a food item that heals 3 [[Hitpoints]] when eaten. It is used as an ingredient in [[Cooking]] but can also be ground to [[chocolate dust]] using a [[pestle and mortar]] or a [[knife]], which is required for the [[Plague City]] quest.

The chocolate bar can be added to a cake with 50 [[Cooking]] to create a chocolate cake.

You can find a chocolate bar spawning in the [[Cooks' Guild]], [[Zanaris]], or in The [[Culinaromancer's Chest]] during and after the [[Recipe for Disaster]] quest, however the chest has low supply which respawns slowly. You can also buy it from [[Funch's Fine Groceries]] located in the [[Grand Tree|The Grand Tree]], for 12 gp each. You can buy chocolate bars from each of the bakers' stalls in [[Ardougne]] market place for 12 gp; their stocks are 7 and 9. You can buy 1 chocolate bar from the food store in Port Sarim for 10gp each. You can buy 25 chocolate bars from [[Rok's Chocs Box]] in [[Nardah]] for 10gp each.
